// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2286 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: dce08b5a-8e21-5333-b540-ec14b3c594ef

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:11* OR ImageFileName = *debian:12* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
